the field is populated by two(2) consecutive characters for each keystroke  
(type ZooBeans and ZZooooBBeeaannss appears). Added to this, an error message  
comes up stating that "Name cannot be empty"  
  
Included in Error from .log, and configuration details taken close to time of  
error occurance.
